Package org.openbel.framework.common.external

Contains support for storing and retrieving types from the filesystem.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CachingExternalizable Describes a reference type that can be stored and retrieved from object I/O.
 

Class Summary
ExternalType This class provides a skeletal implementation of the CachingExternalizable interface to minize the effort needed to externalize a type.
ReadCache Read operation caching mechanism associated with CachingExternalizable.
WriteCache Write operation caching mechanism associated with CachingExternalizable.
